% Expected: Quote handling works correctly
% Category: 37_string_edge_cases
% Priority: P1 - String handling

.kg create test_str_quotes
.kg use test_str_quotes

% Strings with escaped quotes
+messages[(1, "He said \"hello\""), (2, "It's fine"), (3, "A 'quote' here")].

?- messages(Id, Msg).

